# Canonical analysis-scope exclusions for AI agents working in this repository.
#
# These rules are for codebase discovery and reading only. They do not authorize
# deleting support or skipping validation when a task explicitly touches an
# excluded area.
#
# Keep shared core files in scope even when they mention excluded features, for
# example:
# - Cargo.toml
# - src/config/**
# - src/providers/mod.rs
# - src/channels/mod.rs
# - src/channels/traits.rs
# - docs/providers-reference.md
# - docs/channels-reference.md
#
# For mixed files that remain in scope, prefer the relevant Gemini/OpenRouter,
# Discord/WhatsApp, and Linux/macOS paths. Skip unrelated Windows/Android
# branches unless the task explicitly requires them.

# English-only docs profile
CONTRIBUTING.el.md
docs/i18n/**
docs/vi/**
